    "updated_at": "2015-10-21T15:05:07Z",
    "body": "Hmm I think we should not delay the showing of WebContents, it will leave users with empty window when loading slow remote pages, and when errors happens nothing will show. And if developers don't want to show blank page on startup they can just hide the window and show it after page has finished loading, this is a trick already taken by many developers.\n"
